{"title":"Scarab Cycles Paramo Integrated and New Wolf Tooth Headset","link":"https://theradavist.com/scarab-cycles-paramo-integrated/","date":1710511987000,"content":"<p><img width=\"4754\" height=\"3169\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_8.jpeg?fit=1200,3169&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_8.jpeg?w=4754&amp;quality=75 4754w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_8.jpeg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_8.jpeg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_8.jpeg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_8.jpeg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_8.jpeg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>Colombia’s <a href=\"https://scarabcycles.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Scarab Cycles</a> announced a new model today, dubbed the <a href=\"https://scarabcycles.com/paramo-integrated/\" target=\"_blank\">Paramo Integrated</a>. This model expands the Paramo family of gravel bikes and uses the ENVE IN-Route system with the ENVE Gravel IN-Route Fork and an all-new <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;merchant_id=1f8f513b-b98b-4cf0-abf5-e477c8747e9c&amp;website_id=6ec3743b-a948-4c16-9d12-4b79ac107f25&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwolftoothcomponents.com%2F\" target=\"_blank\">Wolf Tooth integrated headset</a>. Let’s check it out below.<span></span></p>\n<p><img width=\"4340\" height=\"2893\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_14.jpeg?fit=1200,2893&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_14.jpeg?w=4340&amp;quality=75 4340w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_14.jpeg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_14.jpeg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_14.jpeg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_14.jpeg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_14.jpeg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /><img width=\"6000\" height=\"4000\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_4.jpeg?fit=1200,4000&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_4.jpeg?w=6000&amp;quality=75 6000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_4.jpeg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_4.jpeg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_4.jpeg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_4.jpeg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_4.jpeg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>Named after the stunning high-altitude landscapes of Colombia, the Paramo Integrated is made in El Retiro, a charming town on the outskirts of Medellín. The Paramo region is known for its tough conditions—thin air, unpredictable weather, and strong winds. Cycling there is a real challenge…</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"6000\" height=\"4000\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_6.jpeg?fit=1200,4000&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_6.jpeg?w=6000&amp;quality=75 6000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_6.jpeg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_6.jpeg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_6.jpeg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_6.jpeg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_6.jpeg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>The latest offering in the line, Paramo Integrated joins our standard Paramo design as well as the Paramo Ultra, which was created for increased tire clearance and the most rugged exploration. Paramo Integrated is a streamlined model that offers some of the most cutting edge technologies produced by Scarab and our partners.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"6000\" height=\"4000\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_3.jpeg?fit=1200,4000&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_3.jpeg?w=6000&amp;quality=75 6000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_3.jpeg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_3.jpeg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_3.jpeg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_3.jpeg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_3.jpeg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"6000\" height=\"4000\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_1.jpeg?fit=1200,4000&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_1.jpeg?w=6000&amp;quality=75 6000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_1.jpeg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_1.jpeg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_1.jpeg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_1.jpeg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_1.jpeg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>“Wolf Tooth has been quietly working on a clean headset solution for integrated cockpits, here in our Minnesota machine shop, with best-in- class stack height, weight, and internal sealing,” said Wolf Tooth Marketing Manager Zach Dolinaj. “We’ve admired Scarab and their custom steel bikes for years.</p>\n<p>When we learned that Scarab was building a Paramo Integrated with this cockpit for Philly Bike Expo, we knew that this was the perfect opportunity to show off a prototype of our new integrated headset.”</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"3845\" height=\"2563\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_16.jpeg?fit=1200,2563&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_16.jpeg?w=3845&amp;quality=75 3845w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_16.jpeg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_16.jpeg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_16.jpeg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_16.jpeg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_16.jpeg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"6000\" height=\"4000\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_12.jpeg?fit=1200,4000&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_12.jpeg?w=6000&amp;quality=75 6000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_12.jpeg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_12.jpeg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_12.jpeg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_12.jpeg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_Premium-Integrated-Headset_12.jpeg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Paramo Integrated</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Tire Clearance: 700c x 48mm</li>\n<li>Enve Gravel IN-Route fork</li>\n<li>Fork cargo mounts</li>\n<li>Wolf Tooth headset</li>\n<li>UDH Dropouts</li>\n<li>T47 Bottom bracket</li>\n<li>MSRP: starting from $3,600 frameset</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>About this special Paramo</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Paint Finish: Marble</li>\n<li>ENVE SES AR handlebar</li>\n<li>Painted in-house by Scarab</li>\n<li>Anodizing on Wolf Tooth components by <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/ashley.anodized.it/\" target=\"_blank\">Ashley.Anodized.it.</a></li>\n<li>Production integrated headsets will be offered in standard Wolf Tooth color pallete.</li>\n<li>ENVE SES 3.4 wheels</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Check out more at <a href=\"https://scarabcycles.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Scarab Cycles</a> and see our extensive coverage of the brand in our related archives below!</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/scarab-cycles-paramo-integrated/\">Scarab Cycles Paramo Integrated and New Wolf Tooth Headset</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"9a0752fc97e4a567cbf6bd424cb131955d91bf716332c9624638f2a72e31732b","category":"Cycling"}